Package kbp2013.managedocuments

This package contains classes to retrieve and normalize KB documents and components before sending them to the API or using them.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    checkSuggestion
    This class implements various methods for query corrections
    DocumentNormalizer
    This class is intended to normalize documents from KBP Corpus to make them compatible with Wikimeta API
    ExpandAbbreviation
    This class expands abbreviations according to "abbreviations" mapping file ex: Boulder, CO --> Boulder, Colorado
    IndexedDocumentCollection
    This class retrieves a document from the KBP collection using Lucene index.
    NormalizedWebDoc
    This class hosts various methods for cleaning web docs: - remove | replace web special strings (ex: smileys) - remove | replace HTML reserved chars (ex: &)
    QueryProcessing
    Class that applies various normalizations to query word sequence
    SpellingCorrector
    This class corrects spelling mistakes using "spelling_mistakes" mapping file ex: soctland --> Scotland
